  <series>MU3E_FPGA_IP</series>
  <version>1.0.0</version>
  <description>CMSIS-SVD description of the histogram bin memory aperture. This file intentionally models the bin RAM as a read-only register window so the MF stack can expose it in a standard CMSIS-SVD tree while preserving clear separation from the control/status CSR window.</description>
